{
  "stem": "1222.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They used to send me with  the horse-- with the horse and the cows for the pasture there, to give them food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What happened-- they did not go ahead, and it never blowed up when they sent me there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They probably-- they didn't want to hurt me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They saw that I'm weak, and they didn't-- you know, they watched me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They should be there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't wear any ammunition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My friend, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was wearing a gun and he was blowing up a lot of stuff, and I would say-- I didn't see it, but he killed a lot of-- a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say most-- if all this Holocaust-- what they were there in the front and knew whatever it was all over the world-- If it's not the Russians, would be very few Holocausts left.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only one liberated was-- is the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not a Communist, but I have salute to the Russians because we wouldn't be alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was taken to hospital in Rovno.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When it was taken away, the Rovno, the first day they were bumping because we didn't have no doctors there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took me and they kept me in the hospital almost six weeks, and they brought me shape.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after that, I was three months back in my small town, but they took away our house and they give it to me next to the police station.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were watching me like a rock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Me, my friend was in the police force.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were watching me like a rock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After that, I saw sooner or later Ukrainians were going to kill me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because after they hanged up the 20 people, they saw that-- that we were the witnesses.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
